hifiberry-autorec (0.1.5) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add man pages for all tools (autorecord, cue_creator, pause_analyzer, vu_meter)
  * Renamed boundary_finder to cue_creator
  * Added --recursive flag for subdirectory processing in cue_creator
  * Added automatic directory detection in cue_creator
  * Added .txt info files with timing analysis and MusicBrainz adjustments
  * Fix --duration 0 to mean unlimited recording (prevent premature exit)
  * Fix --source parameter to actually connect to specified PipeWire source
  * Add validation for PipeWire sources (exit with error if source doesn't exist)
  * Extracted wavfile, audio_analysis, and cuefile modules for better code organization

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Fri, 07 Feb 2026 07:30:00 +0000

hifiberry-autorec (0.1.4) stable; urgency=medium

  * Added adaptive pause detector for song boundary detection
  * Automatically learns noise floor during groove-in
  * Displays current song number during recording
  * Adaptive thresholds based on song length patterns

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Thu, 06 Feb 2026 23:30:00 +0000

hifiberry-autorec (0.1.3) stable; urgency=medium

  * Added periodic song detection via Shazam during recording
  * New --detect-interval option to configure detection frequency
  * New --no-shazam option to disable song detection
  * Display detected song info on VU meter
  * Fixed compiler warnings

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Thu, 06 Feb 2026 22:00:00 +0000

hifiberry-autorec (0.1.2) stable; urgency=medium

  * Display current filename in recording status
  * Recording status now shows filename being written

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Thu, 06 Feb 2026 18:00:00 +0000

hifiberry-autorec (0.1.1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Added configuration file support
  * Defaults can now be saved to ~/.state/autorec/defaults.toml
  * New --save-defaults option to save current settings
  * New --show-saved-defaults option to view saved configuration
  * Saved defaults override built-in defaults
  * Command-line options override both saved and built-in defaults

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Thu, 06 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000

